✨ HOUSTON! We are ON for HALLOWEEN! After a few changes to our line up we are excited to announce our Halloween edition Saturday October 28th @resethtx 👻 9PM-2AM with a very different and unique theme and production! You won’t want to miss it 🥼🧪 we are hosting our special resident dj from Miami @kevinreinoso 🎃 bringing in the spooky and mystic vibes we all love to feel down our spine 👨‍🔬 so get ready for an unforgettable night! 

✨Tickets on sale (link in bio) so come dressed up (or not - whatever you want) just make sure you bring your good vibes, dancing shoes and beautiful energy so we can all feel free to flow, together 💃🏻
